title: Nutanix Prism: Protection Domains
agents: nutanix
catalog: virtual/nutanix
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of the different types and state of
 Protection Domains in a Nutanix cluster.
 The desired state for Metro Availability can be configured through wato.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through "Nutanix Prism".

item:
 The name of the protection domain.

discovery:
 One service is created for each protection domain.
